xdg_cache_home(7)

# NAME

xdg_cache_home - XDG base directory for user-specific non-essential cached data

# DESCRIPTION

*$XDG_CACHE_HOME* defines the base directory relative to which user-specific
non-essential data files should be stored.

# DEFAULT

If *$XDG_CACHE_HOME* is either not set or empty, a default equal to
_$HOME/.cache_ should be used.

# SEE ALSO

*basedir-spec*(7)
